com.adobe.cq.social.scf.core

Interface SocialEvent.EventObject

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SocialEvent.BaseEventObject
    Enclosing class:
    SocialEvent<T extends SocialEvent.SocialActions>

    public static interface SocialEvent.EventObject
    Representation of an event object. An activity has a primary object and a target activity. For instance, in the activity, "John added a comment to the article", the object of the activity is "comment".
